{"word":"H6775 - צָמַד - tsâmad - tsaw-mad' - Fasten","slug":"H6775","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צָמַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tsâmad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-mad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fasten"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E6;&#x05DE;&#x05D3; - tsa&#x0302;mad</b> - <i>tsaw-mad'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>link</i>, that is, <i>gird</i>; figuratively to <i>serve</i>, (mentally) <i>contrive: - </i>fasten, frame, join (self)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6776\">H6776</a>, <a href=\"#/H6781\">H6781</a>"}]}